# Cognify V2 — Technical Architecture & Implementation Design

## Overview

Cognify is a **"Chat-in, UX-out"** product: users type queries into a chat input, and instead of text responses, the system generates interactive UI experiences. The architecture is built around a **three-agent LLM pipeline**, a **composable component library** of UI primitives ("Lego blocks"), and a **dynamic renderer** that turns structured JSON specs into live React experiences.

