## 4. Lego Block Component Library (Allowlist)

### Layout Blocks
| Block | Purpose | Nestable? |
|-------|---------|-----------|
| `Stack` | Vertical flex container | ✅ parent |
| `Grid` | CSS grid layout (2-4 columns) | ✅ parent |
| `Tabs` | Tabbed navigation container | ✅ parent |
| `Accordion` | Collapsible sections | ✅ parent |
| `Columns` | Side-by-side columns | ✅ parent |

### Content Blocks
| Block | Purpose | Nestable? |
|-------|---------|-----------|
| `Hero` | Large title + subtitle + optional visual | ❌ leaf |
| `WikiSection` | Heading + rich text body + optional aside | ✅ has `aside` slot |
| `InfoCard` | Highlighted card with title + content | ❌ leaf |
| `StatCard` | Single metric with label + trend | ❌ leaf |
| `Table` | Data table with headers + rows | ❌ leaf |
| `Image` | Image with caption (placeholder/generated) | ❌ leaf |
| `Callout` | Highlighted tip/warning/note box | ❌ leaf |
| `Divider` | Visual separator | ❌ leaf |

### Interactive Blocks
| Block | Purpose | Nestable? |
|-------|---------|-----------|
| `Quiz` | Multi-question quiz with scoring | ❌ leaf |
| `Form` | Input fields that collect user data | ❌ leaf |
| `FileUpload` | CSV/file upload with preview | ❌ leaf |
| `Slider` | Range input for parameters | ❌ leaf |
| `Chart` | Recharts-powered visualization | ❌ leaf |
| `ProgressTracker` | Step indicator for multi-step flows | ❌ leaf |

### Rules
1. **Only these types are allowed.** The validator rejects any `type` not in this list.
2. **Leaf blocks cannot have `children`.** The validator rejects if they do.
3. **Parent blocks must have `children`.** Empty parents are rejected.
4. **Props are validated per-type** using a per-block JSON schema.

